creator: RestroPress
descriptionHtml:
RestroPress order tracking app gives the store owners to manage their orders directly from the mobile/tablet.

The app notifies you for each order you receive and you can easily update the order status on the using this app.

To use this app you need to get the extension for the Order tracking app so that it will allow you to generate your api details to use this APP. Make sure you have RestroPress and RestroPress order tracking plugins are active on your WordPress site to use this APP.
descriptionShort: RestroPress order tracking app allows you to track your orders on the go.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Added table number to orders for dinein orders
Fixed dine in time to display the selected time
